  <brief_title>A Phase 2 Study to Evaluate the Cardiac and Renal Effects of Short Term Treatment With Elamipretide in Patients Hospitalized With Congestion Due to Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2 Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Cardiac and Renal Effects of Short Term Treatment With Elamipretide in Patients Hospitalized With Congestion Due to Heart Failure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
