  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase 2 randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study to evaluate the cardiac
      and renal effects of short term treatment with elamipretide in patients hospitalized with
      congestion due to heart failure
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
